<lyrics>[V1]
 jìng jìng děng dài zhe, qiāo qiāo kū qì zhe.
 1-----------------------------------------------------------------
 shēn shēn zhù fú zhe, wǒ de guó tǔ.
 2-----------------------------------------------------------------
 shēn shēn zhù fú zhe, wǒ de tóng bāo.
 shén a yuàn nǐ de ài, hòu hòu de jiāo guàn.
 jiāo guàn zhè kuài huáng tǔ de, zī rùn měi gè rén de xīn tián.
 jìng jìng děng dài zhe, qiāo qiāo kū qì zhe.
 shēn shēn zhù fú zhe, wǒ de jiā yuán.</lyrics>
<title>jìng jìng děng dài zhe 迦南962</title>
